{"tid":1509550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非請有心理準備要變前線後備軍  當前線人數減少","createTime":"2019-08-27T01:25:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T12:25:01.000Z","uid":229436,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"974778371f5b935d7c4fe1d3d62843ebd912ca24","tid":1509550,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:25:02.000Z","msg":"已經比班廢物捉左我地好多手足<br />\n前線人數會愈來愈少 <br />\n和理非唔想輸 一定要有準備替補前線的準備<br />\n睇定 或者直接準備定裝備 不時之需<br />\n<br />\n唔通你地接受到自己仲係到嘆冷氣 睇住剩番個班勇武比人拉曬但發現自己咩都做唔到 你可以安心？<br />\n去救人去做物資 後勤 都可以<br />\n<br />\n和理非唔可以仲諗住獨善其身 否則你同口交部係無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係要你依家轉變去前線<br />\n但需要你有心理準備 認真諗下你能力內其實仲可以去到咩位 <br />\n<br />\n有人需要你個陣 連和理非都可以即時上場 因為有曬架生<br />\n咁先可以做到草木皆兵<br />\n殺班廢物政府一個措手不及"},{"pid":"c001efe1d9a3a73dcba9c54eb7b042b0e09c9c4a","tid":1509550,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:25:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=655c25da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=0c5c7076\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=fb5c9db3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"d3e9cd2c8219180216a7ab0042ccfadcdff4047b","tid":1509550,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:25:24.000Z","msg":"小知識 - 原來機場控制唔只控制香港D機上落，<br />\n廣洲，深圳，澳門既飛機升降都會受香港指揮影響，搞到D飛升降唔到。。。。<br />\n大家千祈唔好搞到機場控制個班番唔到工啊 會好大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現有文宣集合 (Google Drive)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=ce0dd3ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n請隨便使用，用自己的方法幫忙發送文宣出去，感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LoOsXdt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLoOsXdt.jpg&h=b1104862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">每晚10點</span></strong></span>大家開大嗰窗嗌口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當係抒發下或者互相鼓勵都好<br />\n<br />\n真係有人嗌㗎 唔洗怕醜<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fit.tsoi/videos/189596038709864/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffit.tsoi%2Fvideos%2F189596038709864%2F&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=3125203b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fit.tsoi/videos/189596038709864/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1170684516349159/posts/2398098013607797?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1170684516349159%2Fposts%2F2398098013607797%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=f5229fac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1